description.narrative: UNICEF supported the revitalization of public health and brought attention to the need to increase investment in preventive health care, higher focus on public health, and mental health of young people. UNICEF CO and ROSA contributed to capacity building of immunization programme through several activities: by conducting the regional cold chain maintenance training, Effective Vaccine Management (EVM) training, followed by initiating an assessment of the vaccine and cold-chain management. Vaccine hesitancy assessment was undertaken and vaccine communication strategy and action plan were drafted. Key findings is supporting to further enhance the immunization program in the Maldives. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:15/12/2019
